description:
Friday Night With Jonathan Ross S16E12 Ws Pdtv Xvid-Waters.Avi

A superb episode with Dame Helen Mirren, Simon Pegg discussing his part in the new Star Trek film and some shouty little American girl that I have no idea who she was. 

Plus the great Spandau Ballet talking about getting back together and performing two songs on stage at the end of the show. Worth watching for that alone.
